| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4567 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 56ba6fbe-9a04-5222-95cd-85c3226468d0"
